title: february 27: the discovery of the neutron
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the discovery of the neutron. Then, she remembers how one of alt pop’s most electric duos got their first taste of stardom. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
